  • Packages that use fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.utils 
    Package Description
    fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.core
    Provides all core classes and method to do extraction and listing of mail boxes.
    fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.formattools
    Provides all classes and methods to deal with identification and format conversion tools.
    fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.formattools.rtf
    Provides all classes and methods to de-encapsulate HTML and text from RTF.
    fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.nodes
    Provides all classes and method to create, manage and edit to disk the ArchiveUnits with their metadata.
    fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.store.javamail
    Provides all classes to extract stores with JavaMail library.
    fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.store.microsoft
    Provides all classes to extract stores in Microsoft format.
    fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.store.microsoft.msg
    Provides all classes to implement a Microsoft .msg single message container.
    fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.store.microsoft.pst
    Provides all classes to implement a Microsoft .pst messages container with libpst library.
    fr.gouv.vitam.tools.mailextract.lib.store.microsoft.pst.embeddedmsg
    Provides all classes to implement a Microsoft .pst embedded message extraction with libpst library.
